title: Top Tier Providence: Secretly Cultivate for a Thousand Years

顶级气运，悄悄修炼千年
summary: Top Tier Providence ManhwaBeing reincarnated in a cultivation world, Han Jue realizes that he can live his life like a video game. He can reroll his cultivation potential and connate providence. So, he spends 11 years rerolling for a good one… [Unparalleled: Immortal beauty, top-notch charm] [Destined Sword fanatic: Top-notch Sword Dao aptitude, top-notch Sword Dao comprehension] [Unparalleled Movement Technique: Top-notch movement technique aptitude] [Descendant of the Immortal Emperor: You will receive an unparalleled cultivation technique and 1,000 superior-grade spirit stones] In pursuit of longevity, Han Jue decides to cultivate in a low-profile manner. A thousand years later, generations of cultivators have become history. That is when beings of the immortal world start cleansing the mortal world. Han Jue can no longer hide and has no choice but to take action. Then he realizes, that deities and gods aren’t that powerful after all!
